Jewelry: the return of the (popular?) NES game
-----------------------------------------------------------------

Jewelry is the Haskell remake of the Magic Jewelry game for NES:

  http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Magic_Jewelry

Jewelry depends on the following Haskell packages:

  mutators     - http://github.com/dmatveev/mutators
  oak          - http://github.com/dmatveev/oak
  SDL, SDL-ttf - available on Hackage

Jewelry is bundled with the Liberation Sans font from:

  https://fedorahosted.org/liberation-fonts/

Building:

  ghc --make Jewelry.hs
